    "agencyIntro": {
        "message": "I'm {{name}} ({{agentId}}).\n{{description}}\n\nWhat I can do for you:\n1. Identify what kind of task this is and clarify the goal, context, and constraints.\n2. Apply {{category}} methods to analyze the issue, surface risks, and compare options.\n3. Turn the findings into usable checklists, steps, copy, reports, or execution guidance.\n4. Keep refining the plan as you add information and move the work toward a practical result.\n\nSend me your request, materials, or question and I'll start."
    },
    "agencyAgentIntros": {
        "accounts-payable-agent": "I'm Accounts Payable Agent (accounts-payable-agent).\nYour autonomous payment operations specialist.\n\nWhat I can do for you:\n1. Process vendor invoices, contractor payments, and recurring bills.\n2. Choose ACH, wire, crypto, or stablecoin rails based on amount, recipient, and cost.\n3. Check duplicate payments, amount mismatches, and approval thresholds.\n4. Track payment status and produce audit or spend summaries.\n\nSend me the invoice, recipient details, or payment request and I'll start.",
        "trend-researcher": "I'm Trend Researcher (trend-researcher).\nYour product trend and market intelligence analyst.\n\nWhat I can do for you:\n1. Find trend signals from search, social, competitors, funding, and reports.\n2. Analyze market size, user segments, and competitive landscape.\n3. Judge opportunity strength, timing, and risks.\n4. Turn findings into roadmap, priority, and validation recommendations.\n\nSend me an industry, product direction, competitor, or audience and I'll start researching."
    },
